    <published>2016-09-08T01:24:53.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-09-09T11:36:58.705Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<script src="/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js"> </script><p>或多或少参考的文章(排名不分先后)<br><a href="https://www.futures.moe/writings/configure-nginx-with-security-and-effective-yes-or-no.htm" target="_blank" rel="external">https://www.futures.moe/writings/configure-nginx-with-security-and-effective-yes-or-no.htm</a><br><a href="https://github.com/blackgear/blog_article/blob/master/_posts/optimize-hexo-blog.md" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/blackgear/blog_article/blob/master/_posts/optimize-hexo-blog.md</a><br><a href="https://imququ.com/post/my-nginx-conf-for-security.html" target="_blank" rel="external">https://imququ.com/post/my-nginx-conf-for-security.html</a><br><a href="https://imququ.com/post/my-nginx-conf-for-wpo.html" target="_blank" rel="external">https://imququ.com/post/my-nginx-conf-for-wpo.html</a><br><a href="https://imququ.com/post/http-public-key-pinning.html" target="_blank" rel="external">https://imququ.com/post/http-public-key-pinning.html</a><br><a href="https://falconchen.github.io/2014/06/05/pagespeed-insights-opt/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://falconchen.github.io/2014/06/05/pagespeed-insights-opt/</a><br><a href="http://zhangge.net/5063.html" target="_blank" rel="external">http://zhangge.net/5063.html</a><br><a href="https://github.com/NextMoe/hexo-tag-dplayer/issues/1" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/NextMoe/hexo-tag-dplayer/issues/1</a><br><a href="https://www.google.com" target="_blank" rel="external">https://www.google.com</a><br>………<br>有的我自己都记不清了  </p>
<p>安装+优化部分(Nginx+pagespeed+gzip+http2)  </p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">wget http://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.11.3.tar.gz</div><div class="line">wget http://ftp.openbsd.org/pub/OpenBSD/LibreSSL/libressl-2.4.2.tar.gz </div><div class="line">wget https://github.com/pagespeed/ngx_pagespeed/archive/v1.11.33.3-beta.zip</div><div class="line">tar -zxvf libressl*.tar.gz</div><div class="line">tar -zxvf nginx*.tar.gz</div><div class="line">unzip v1.11.33.3-beta.zip </div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ngx_pagespeed-*-beta/</div><div class="line">wget https://dl.google.com/dl/page-speed/psol/1.11.33.3.tar.gz </div><div class="line">tar -zxvf *.tar.gz</div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> ..</div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> nginx*</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>由于冰喵用的Arch，自己是手动解决一大堆依赖了，想不起来了，所以只能慢慢谷歌咯  </p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">./configure --prefix=/opt/nginx --with-ipv6 --with-http_ssl_module --with-http_v2_module --with-http_realip_module --with-http_addition_module --with-http_sub_module --with-http_dav_module --with-http_flv_module --with-http_mp4_module --with-http_gunzip_module --with-http_gzip_static_module --with-http_auth_request_module --with-http_random_index_module --with-http_secure_link_module --with-http_degradation_module --with-http_stub_status_module --with-openssl=../libressl-2.4.2 --add-module=../ngx_pagespeed-release-1.11.33.2-beta</div><div class="line">make &amp;&amp; make install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>编辑nginx.conf(单站点)<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div><div class="line">40</div><div class="line">41</div><div class="line">42</div><div class="line">43</div><div class="line">44</div><div class="line">45</div><div class="line">46</div><div class="line">47</div><div class="line">48</div><div class="line">49</div><div class="line">50</div><div class="line">51</div><div class="line">52</div><div class="line">53</div><div class="line">54</div><div class="line">55</div><div class="line">56</div><div class="line">57</div><div class="line">58</div><div class="line">59</div><div class="line">60</div><div class="line">61</div><div class="line">62</div><div class="line">63</div><div class="line">64</div><div class="line">65</div><div class="line">66</div><div class="line">67</div><div class="line">68</div><div class="line">69</div><div class="line">70</div><div class="line">71</div><div class="line">72</div><div class="line">73</div><div class="line">74</div><div class="line">75</div><div class="line">76</div><div class="line">77</div><div class="line">78</div><div class="line">79</div><div class="line">80</div><div class="line">81</div><div class="line">82</div><div class="line">83</div><div class="line">84</div><div class="line">85</div><div class="line">86</div><div class="line">87</div><div class="line">88</div><div class="line">89</div><div class="line">90</div><div class="line">91</div><div class="line">92</div><div class="line">93</div><div class="line">94</div><div class="line">95</div><div class="line">96</div><div class="line">97</div><div class="line">98</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">user  nobody;</div><div class="line">worker_processes  1;</div><div class="line">events &#123;</div><div class="line">    worker_connections  1024;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">http &#123;</div><div class="line">    include       mime.types;</div><div class="line">    default_type  application/octet-stream;</div><div class="line">	server_tokens   off;</div><div class="line">    sendfile        on;</div><div class="line">    tcp_nopush     on;</div><div class="line">	tcp_nodelay        on;</div><div class="line">    #keepalive_timeout  0;</div><div class="line">    keepalive_timeout  60;</div><div class="line">	gzip on;</div><div class="line">	gzip_static on;</div><div class="line">	gzip_http_version 1.1;</div><div class="line">	gzip_vary on;</div><div class="line">	gzip_min_length 256;</div><div class="line">	gzip_buffers 16 8k;</div><div class="line">	gzip_comp_level 9;</div><div class="line">	gzip_proxied any;</div><div class="line">	gzip_types</div><div class="line">    text/xml application/xml application/atom+xml application/rss+xml application/xhtml+xml image/svg+xml</div><div class="line">    text/javascript application/javascript application/x-javascript</div><div class="line">    text/x-json application/json application/x-web-app-manifest+json</div><div class="line">    text/css text/plain text/x-component</div><div class="line">    font/opentype application/x-font-ttf application/vnd.ms-fontobject</div><div class="line">    image/x-icon;</div><div class="line">	gzip_disable msie6;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">#http跳转到https</div><div class="line">server &#123;</div><div class="line">	listen       80 ;</div><div class="line">	listen		 [::]:80;</div><div class="line">	server_name 你的域名;</div><div class="line">	rewrite ^/(.*) https://你的域名$1 permanent;</div><div class="line">	access_log off;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">#https配置</div><div class="line">server &#123;</div><div class="line">	#开启pagespeed</div><div class="line">	pagespeed on;</div><div class="line">	#pagespeed缓存目录</div><div class="line">	pagespeed FileCachePath /var/ngx_pagespeed_cache;</div><div class="line">	#开启转换 png转jpeg转webp</div><div class="line">	pagespeed EnableFilters convert_png_to_jpeg,convert_jpeg_to_webp;</div><div class="line">	#预解析DNS查询</div><div class="line">	pagespeed EnableFilters insert_dns_prefetch;</div><div class="line">	#重写CSS，首先加载渲染页面的CSS规则 </div><div class="line">	pagespeed EnableFilters prioritize_critical_css;</div><div class="line">	#把多个JavaScript文件合并成一个JavaScript文件(减少对请求的文件量，对站点速度有帮助)</div><div class="line">	pagespeed EnableFilters combine_javascript;  </div><div class="line">	# 把多个CSS文件合并成一个CSS文件(减少对请求的文件量，对站点速度有帮助)</div><div class="line">	pagespeed EnableFilters combine_css;</div><div class="line">	#隐藏nginx信息</div><div class="line">	server_tokens   off;</div><div class="line">	#该listen中包含了 默认站点 启用ssl 启用https2 启用TCP Fast Open</div><div class="line">    listen        443 default ssl http2 fastopen=3 reuseport;</div><div class="line">	listen		 [::]:443 default ssl http2 fastopen=3 reuseport;</div><div class="line">	</div><div class="line">    server_name 你的域名;</div><div class="line">	#限制在了只有tlsv1.2，我想只要不是古董浏览器都支持吧？</div><div class="line">	ssl_protocols TLSv1.2;</div><div class="line">	#证书，我使用的letsencrypt</div><div class="line">	ssl_certificate /etc/letsencrypt/ecc/morz.org_ecc/fullchain.cer;</div><div class="line">	ssl_certificate_key /etc/letsencrypt/ecc/morz.org_ecc/morz.org.key;</div><div class="line">	#ssl的前向加密，建议部署</div><div class="line">	#openssl dhparam -out morz.160909.pem 4096</div><div class="line">	#配置好的上8192，垃圾的上2048，我这vps妥妥中间吧</div><div class="line">	ssl_dhparam          /home/morz.org.pem;</div><div class="line">	ssl_session_cache    shared:SSL:10m;</div><div class="line">	ssl_session_timeout  60m;</div><div class="line">	ssl_session_tickets      on;</div><div class="line">	ssl_prefer_server_ciphers  on;</div><div class="line">	#OCSP Stapling 用于验证证书，具体看维基百科（https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OCSP_stapling）</div><div class="line">    ssl_stapling               on;</div><div class="line">	resolver                   114.114.114.114 valid=300s;</div><div class="line">    resolver_timeout           10s;</div><div class="line">	#使用的加密套件</div><div class="line">	ssl_ciphers &quot;EECDH+CHACHA20:EECDH+CHACHA20-draft:EECDH+AES128:RSA+AES128:EECDH+AES256:RSA+AES256:EECDH+3DES:RSA+3DES&quot;;</div><div class="line">	add_header X-Frame-Options SAMEORIGIN;</div><div class="line">	#HSTS 强制https，在遇到中间人的时候浏览器强制拒绝访问</div><div class="line">	add_header Strict-Transport-Security &quot;max-age=31536000; includeSubdomains; preload&quot;;</div><div class="line">	add_header               X-Frame-Options deny;</div><div class="line">    add_header               X-Content-Type-Options nosniff;</div><div class="line">	#HPKP 服务端指定某CA证书 没指定的证书将被拒绝访问</div><div class="line">	#此处请参考https://imququ.com/post/http-public-key-pinning.html</div><div class="line">	add_header Public-Key-Pins &apos;pin-sha256=&quot;fVZ1UlYWgPZvUe9THLBBeg1pNN7LF4HI373EsQhUAdE=&quot;; pin-sha256=&quot;YLh1dUR9y6Kja30RrAn7JKnbQG/uEtLMkBgFF2Fuihg=&quot;; max-age=2592000; includeSubDomains&apos;;</div><div class="line">	location / &#123;</div><div class="line">		root  /站点目录;</div><div class="line">		index index.html;</div><div class="line">	&#125;</div><div class="line">	location ~ \.(js|css|ico)$ &#123;</div><div class="line">           root /站点目录;</div><div class="line">           expires 7d;</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>#未完待续 </p>
]]></content>
    
